    "display_name": "Independent Farmer",
    "long_instructions": "## Carlos Mendes, Independent Farmer\r\n\r\n**Location:** Baramati, India\r\n\r\n**Workplace:** Family-Owned Farm\r\n\r\n**Expertise:** Crop management, soil health, sustainable farming\r\n\r\n**How I Use AI:** \"FarmVibes.AI gives me real-time insights on soil moisture, weather forecasts, and the best times to plant. By using AI, I can conserve water, reduce fertilizer waste, and improve my crop yield, making my farm more sustainable and profitable.\" </p>\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\n### Do This:\r\n\r\n1. Use AI Chat to conduct the interview and take notes on their responses. Ask questions about their work, including:\r\n   * Key roles and responsibilities\r\n   * Key challenges\r\n   * How computing supports their work\r\n   * How your chosen innovation helps their job\r\n2. Summarize key insights in your activity guide.",
